{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SharedWorker.port","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker/port","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><em><code>port</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker/error_event\"><code>SharedWorker: error event</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Web Workers API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>DedicatedWorkerGlobalScope</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorker\"><code>ServiceWorker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorkerGlobalScope\"><code>SharedWorkerGlobalScope</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerLocation\"><code>WorkerLocation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator\"><code>WorkerNavigator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>A propriedade <code><strong>port</strong></code> do&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a> retorna um objeto <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a> usado para comunicar e controlar o&nbsp;shared worker.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">myWorker.port;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor","title":"Valor","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Um objeto <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O snippet de código a seguir mostra a criação de um objeto SharedWorker usando o construtor&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker ()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> . Vários scripts podem acessar o worker através de um objeto do tipo&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a> , usando a propriedade SharedWorker.port &nbsp;— A porta é iniciada usando o método&nbsp;<code>start()</code>&nbsp;.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> myWorker <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SharedWorker</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'worker.js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmyWorker<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>port<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">start</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Veja um exemplo completo&nbsp;<a class=\"external external-icon\" href=\"https://github.com/mdn/simple-shared-worker\" rel=\" noopener\">Basic shared worker example</a> (<a class=\"external external-icon\" href=\"https://mdn.github.io/simple-shared-worker/\" rel=\" noopener\">run shared worker</a>.)</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#dom-sharedworker-port\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'AbstractWorker.onerror' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>No change from <a href=\"about:unknown\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'Unknown' specification\">Unknown</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"about:unknown#dom-sharedworker-port\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\">Unknown<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'AbstractWorker.onerror' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-\">Desconhecido</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Support</td>\n   <td>4</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/29\" title=\"Released on 2014-04-29.\">29.0</a> (29.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>10.60</td>\n   <td>5<br>\n    <span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span> 6.1</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Firefox OS (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>33.0 (33.0)</td>\n   <td>2.1</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>11.5</td>\n   <td>5.1<br>\n    <span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span> 7.1</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>The <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker\"><code>SharedWorker</code></a> interface it belongs to.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"A propriedade port do SharedWorker retorna um objeto MessagePort usado para comunicar e controlar o shared worker.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SharedWorker.port","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"SharedWorker.port","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"SharedWorker.port","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/sharedworker/port","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/sharedworker/port/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker","title":"SharedWorker"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/SharedWorker/port","title":"SharedWorker.port"}],"pageTitle":"SharedWorker.port - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}